{
  "texts": [
    "This innovation may reshape the disposition of learning, particularly in language education, by transforming teacher-centric and passive learning environments, with more linear types of learning interactions, into dynamic, engaging experiences that are technologically driven.",
    "But this is contingent on what Borgmann [19] suggests is the capacity of technology to enrich human life, not undermine it.",
    "Beyond a passive relationship with technology, active and critical engagement with technology and learning would appear to be the key.Conventionally, language learning resources, including textbooks and digital content, have been static and not promoted active and critical engagement.",
    "Students would learn information and then attempt to do exercises or quizzes to test their knowledge.",
    "Generative AI reshapes this learning paradigm by merging learning with evaluation in a dynamic and individualized manner."
  ]
}